1
00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:02,042
O ka tswa o utlwile ka Buka ya ga Momone,

2
00:00:02,042 --> 00:00:04,542
mme o ka nna wa gakgamala
gore tota e bua ka ga eng.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,125
Fa godimo,

4
00:00:05,125 --> 00:00:08,584
ke  polelo ya dingwaga tse
1000 ya tlhabologo e kgolo .

5
00:00:08,584 --> 00:00:10,000
Mme mo boteng jwa yone,

6
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,542
ke ka ga batho ba ba lekang go ithuta
ka Jeso Keresete le go mo latela.

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:17,542
E simolola kwa Jerusalema e ka
nna ka 600 BC fa moporofeti a ne a

8
00:00:17,542 --> 00:00:20,667
tlhagiswa ke Modimo go tshaba
tshenyego e e gomagometsang toropo.

9
00:00:20,667 --> 00:00:23,209
Ene le lelwapa la gagwe ba
kaelwa go kgabaganyetsa kwa

10
00:00:23,209 --> 00:00:26,000
moseja ga lewatle go ya kwa
jaanong go bidiwang  Amerika.

11
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,876
Batho ba a gola mme bofelong ba
ikgaoganya go nna ditshaba tse

12
00:00:28,876 --> 00:00:31,751
pedi tse di kgolo tse di nang
le dinako tsa ntwa le kagiso.

13
00:00:31,751 --> 00:00:35,459
Botshelo jwa bone bo ka go tlhotlholetsa
go nna le tumelo mo go Jeso Keresete,

14
00:00:35,459 --> 00:00:38,250
go tshegetsa ditaelo tsa Gagwe,
le go direla ba bangwe.

15
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:40,667
Buka ya ga Momone e na
le mafoko a a molemo a

16
00:00:40,667 --> 00:00:43,584
baporofeti ba ba neng ba
paka ka go tla ga Mmoloki.

17
00:00:43,584 --> 00:00:46,167
E tlhomamisa boammaaruri
jwa Baebele le bopaki

18
00:00:46,167 --> 00:00:48,667
jwa gore Jeso Keresete ke Morwa wa Modimo;

19
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:49,876
gore O tshidile, a swa,

20
00:00:49,876 --> 00:00:53,292
mme a fenya loso le sebe ka ntlha
ya mongwe le mongwe wa rona.

21
00:00:53,292 --> 00:00:57,083
Ke ka lebaka le e bidiwang “Kgolagano
e nngwe ya ga Jeso Keresete.”​

22
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,584
Bonnete,

23
00:00:57,584 --> 00:01:01,501
setlhoa sa tiragalo ya buka ke
ketelo ya ga Jeso Keresete go

24
00:01:01,501 --> 00:01:05,292
batho ba Amerika morago ga
tsogo ya Gagwe kwa Jerusalema.

25
00:01:05,292 --> 00:01:10,125
O ruta efangele ya Gagwe, o fodisa balwetse,
le go segofatsa bana ba bone.

26
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,417
Mme seo ke tshimologo fela ya polelo.

27
00:01:12,417 --> 00:01:16,167
Ditlamorago tsa nnete tsa Buka
ya ga Momone ke ka fa e ka go

28
00:01:16,167 --> 00:01:20,292
thusang ka teng ka dikgwetlho tse
o lebaganang le tsone gompieno.

29
00:01:20,292 --> 00:01:21,459
O ka bona kgomotso,

30
00:01:21,459 --> 00:01:25,834
kaelo le go ithuta go nna motho yo
o botoka le yo o itumetseng thata.

31
00:01:25,834 --> 00:01:26,709
Bogolo-segolo,

32
00:01:26,709 --> 00:01:30,083
o ka atamela gaufi le Mmoloki
wa gago Jeso Keresete.

